# UI stack: Base UI

This project uses **Base UI** (`@base-ui/react`), not Radix UI.

- Use Base UI primitives and patterns when adding or modifying UI components.
- Do not suggest or use Radix UI packages (e.g. `@radix-ui/react-*`).
- Shadcn components in this repo are built on Base UI (see e.g. `src/components/ui/button.tsx` using `@base-ui/react/button`).
